Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Documentary papyrus
Description: Documentary papyrus featuring two lines followed by a date (17 Pharmonthi of a year 34), detached in the third line. Of this ending of text, one can only say that it dealt with problems related to corn (line 3), though the general direction completely escapes us.
